{"tid":395522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬時亨籲勿妄自判斷張貼奚落語句人士身份","createTime":"2017-09-11T00:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T04:59:21.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66cbcab2c01a3104388e0326794197c817f0f07f","tid":395522,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:35:06.000Z","msg":"而家拉到劉曉波就龜縮，上星期好撚串架屎坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=963582&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D963582%26csid%3D261_341&d=5ay%2F%2FW2H93mD75sgs%2Fvw04zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=90cbf046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=963582&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬時亨籲勿妄自判斷張貼奚落語句人士身份<br />\n11.09.2017 08:30<br />\n<br />\n教育大學校董會主席馬時亨在本台節目說，校內民主牆出現奚落蔡若蓮及劉曉波、劉霞的字句，校方仍未知張貼的人的身份，期望各方不要妄自判斷，即使張貼的人真的是教大學生，亦只是個別事件，呼籲不要牽連其他學生，大學必定會按規矩處理。<br />\n<br />\n馬時亨呼籲「教育歸教育、政治歸政治」，說校長張仁良不是政治人物，但有言論對他上綱上線，對他很不公平。張仁良承認近日收到電郵，說事件令他們對教育大學的畢業生有不同看法，他會在風波過後，向校長、辦學團體等多作解釋。"},{"pid":"c27d5b7bf18f264a0d607f93741e7ec9f4d7a01b","tid":395522,"uid":51828,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:37:24.000Z","msg":"正一狗黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be704789765bc1232f98c00939296a1353f64e40","tid":395522,"uid":122,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5