<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759bc535b3bc6c48b68ff8c36e16e45778b59659","tid":395522,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:53:24.000Z","msg":"鬼拍後尾枕得半粒鐘通知學生會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45ec1feb305aed6d7a6b54344f7d67e42a03700","tid":395522,"uid":29295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:54:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬼拍後尾枕得半粒鐘通知學生會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要凌晨五點幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43adc14ef9cd2d8765cffde5f9d1ceed46188d9d","tid":395522,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:56:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母早幾日唔係咁講架，轉軚轉得咁撚快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a4ac317ba5841fb2a39b35a87ba4ddf65790bc","tid":395522,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:56:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撚狗咁撚</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e22daa98e3c7a3767d3eecfe02f426780e6c22","tid":395522,"uid":134834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:57:32.000Z","msg":"大家唔好再推蔡若蓮D BIN C POST得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地已經好慘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f020d00fc7a6e2d4fcb46d2a3eb178f70596a1","tid":395522,"uid":49316,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:02:20.00